data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 1.5 story home situated on one acre of land with that country living feel. This home has plenty to offer with four bedrooms, possibility of a fifth non-conforming room, 2.5 baths and an open concept living space. The home features granite countertops, updated fixtures, plenty of closet space, water softener, a newer HVAC system and a newer roof. There is plenty of space to entertain and live comfortably. The two-car detached garage has a space above the garage that can be accessed with steps from the back. Above the garage, you will find a spacious area that can be made into a game room, a get-away spot or other endless possibilities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional property.
